<HI>Green&s;hields</HI> out of Pri&s;on AND Toleration &s;ettled in <HI>SCOTLAND,</HI> OR THE CASE OF Mr. Green&s;hields, Farther Examin'd. WITH Some Enquiry into the Mi&s;takes about that Affair, which have &s;o much impos'd upon the Pre&s;ent Age.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed for N. CLIFF, at the <HI>Golden Candle&s;tick</HI> in <HI>Cheap&s;ide</HI> near <HI>Mercers Chapel.</HI> MDCCX.</P>
